        <br />
        “CEA is honored to receive this TSEA award, and we are especially thrilled that our customers, the exhibiting companies of the International CES, selected us as their favorite trade show,” said Gary Shapiro, president and CEO, CEA. “I could not be more proud of Karen Chupka for her Best Show Manager award. Karen oversees every aspect of the world’s largest consumer technology tradeshow, and her leadership and dedication make the International CES a global success.”<br />
