        <div class="sub-content-header">MyCES and the Online Exhibitor Directory Generate More than a Million Company Listing Views</div>
        <span class="smallText">Jan 08, 2011 02:23:05</span>
        
        <P><IMG hspace=5 align=right src="/images/content/MY_CES_2k10.gif" width=128 height=85>There’s no doubt attendees know where to find information about exhibitors quickly and easily.&nbsp;Together, <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/myCES.asp">MyCES</A> and the <A href="http://ces12.mapyourshow.com/3_0/search.cfm?">online exhibitor directory</A> have generated more than a million company listing views and over 160,000 sales leads, proving their usefulness as key attendee planning tools.&nbsp;In record numbers, attendees have viewed exhibitor information as they log onto CESweb.org or accessed their personal MyCES agenda planner while on-site at the show. Both digital applications provide attendees with real-time information and gives them a bigger glimpse into exhibitor products and services.<BR></P>
    
